## üí° Usage Examples

### Quick Health Check
```bash
netpicker health
netpicker whoami --json | jq .
```

### Device Operations
```bash
# List first 10 devices
netpicker devices list --limit 10

# Show device details in JSON
netpicker devices show --ip 192.168.1.1 --json

# Create a new device
